  <summary>12/11/2001--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to establish, for a limited time period, deductions and credits for commercial and residential properties using specified energy efficient construction or reconstruction approaches (component or performance-based). Sets forth provisions concerning allocation of deductions for public property. Requires the Secretary of the Treasury to establish specified certification and compliance procedures.</summary>
